        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Note (due to Russ Mann): one can also give a \"nonconstructive\" argument. Let N be a large positive integer. For b E (N?, N3), the number of 3-digit base-b palindromes in the range (b2, N° - 1] is at least",
