        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "since there is a palindrome in each interval kb, (k + 1)b - 1] for k = b,...,b - 1. Thus the average number of bases for which a number in [1, N6 - 1] is at least",
        "bbox": [
          0.12781955212030868,
