        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "for some constant c > 0. Take N so that the right side exceeds 2002; then at least one number in (1,N6 - 1] is a base-b palindrome for at least 2002 values of b.",
        "bbox": [
